cc:Work.dc:title: Three Film Strips - Poster Frame
cc:Work.dc:description: I think that user sergSB uploads some great clipart, but it is often monolingual and not so well suited to general use. (I imagined this could be used for a film festival poster/banner or some sort of movie night, etc) So I hope sergSB doesn't mind if I upload more general use remixes of the provided clipart, so that they can be more widely enjoyed :)
